{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/fan-work-berupa-lagu-dari-adriana-figueroa/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Fan Work Berupa Lagu dari Adriana Figueroa!","content":"<p><em>Fan work</em> adalah karya buatan <em>fans</em> yang dibuat untuk mengungkapkan perasaan mereka terhadap cerita atau karakter tertentu yang disukai, atau bahkan hanya sekedar memuaskan “fantasi pribadi” mereka untuk dinikmati oleh <em>fans</em> lainnya. Biasanya ketika mendengar kata <em>fan work</em>, pikiran kita akan tertuju pada tulisan berupa <em>fan fiction</em>, gambar berupa komik maupun <em>fan art</em> saja. Namun tahukah kamu kalau ada juga<em> fan work</em> yang berupa lagu?</p>\n<p>Adriana Figueroa adalah salah satu youtuber yang cukup populer dalam menyanyikan lagu-lagu <em>fan work</em> dari <em>western fandom</em> hingga telah mencapai 400 ribu <em>subscriber</em>. Ia lahir tanggal <a href=\"https://www.famousbirthdays.com/people/adriana-figueroa.html\">30 Desember 1992</a>, dan seperti kebanyakan youtuber terkenal, ia lahir dan besar di Amerika Serikat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47233\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47233\" data-attachment-id=\"47233\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yuk-tonton-gadis-gadis-kecil-menari/attachment/ariana1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ariana1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Adriana Figueroa (Sumber: Facebook)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47233\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47233\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Adriana Figueroa (Sumber: Facebook)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pada tahun 2010, Adriana mengunggah karya pertamanya melalui youtube dengan nama akun <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAHPCNxU4A-TUV-lnu7u4tA\">adrisaurus</a>. Lagu tersebut berjudul <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Dj9kgNNHck\">Fragrance of Dark Coffee</a> yang menggunakan tema dari game Ace Attorney dengan lirik yang ia tulis sendiri berdasarkan karakter Godot dari fandom tersebut. Kemudian ia terus membuat cukup banyak lagu bertema Ace Attorney yang lebih banyak dibandingkan lagu dari fandom lain, menunjukkan bahwa sepertinya Adriana memang berdedikasi pada fandom tersebut.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47236\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47236\" data-attachment-id=\"47236\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yuk-tonton-gadis-gadis-kecil-menari/attachment/ariana4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ariana4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Godot (Sumber: gametimewm)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47236\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47236\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Godot (Sumber: gametimewm)</p></div></p>\n<p>Popularitas Adriana mulai berkembang saat ia mengunggah lagu bertema Legend of Zelda: Majora’s Mask yang berjudul <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mPq9K7M0-XE\">Song of Healing</a>. Video tersebut adalah video pertamanya yang mencapai jumlah satu juta penonton.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47237\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47237\" data-attachment-id=\"47237\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yuk-tonton-gadis-gadis-kecil-menari/attachment/ariana5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ariana5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Legend of Zelda: Majora’s Mask (Sumber: zeldadungeon)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47237\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47237\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Legend of Zelda: Majora’s Mask (Sumber: zeldadungeon)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kemudian popularitas Adriana kembali melejit pada tahun 2011 setelah ia mengunggah video lagu bertemakan Hunger Games yang berjudul The Hanging Tree. Tak tanggung-tanggung, ia mendapatkan enam juta lebih penonton.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uKrCE1aYz7o\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Ia membuat melodi dan aransemen sendiri berdasarkan lirik yang terdapat dalam novel terakhir dari seri Hunger Games. Fans seri tersebut merespon baik aransemen milik Adriana. Namun setelah film official The Hunger Games: Mockingjay rilis, video tersebut sempat hilang terkena kasus copy right karena dalam film tersebut terdapat lagu yang sama meskipun memiliki melodi yang berbeda. Untungnya kemudian video tersebut kembali muncul dan bisa dinikmati hingga kini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47234\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47234\" data-attachment-id=\"47234\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yuk-tonton-gadis-gadis-kecil-menari/attachment/ariana2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ariana2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Adriana On Camera (Sumber: Youtube)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47234\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47234\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Adriana On Camera (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi jika mesti membandikan popularitas semua lagu yang ia unggah, tentu lagu yang paling terkenal hingga mendapatkan embilan juta lebih penonton tak lain dan tak bukan datang dari fandom Undertale.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HW-Jr4M4w90\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Selain lagu-lagu yang memang melodi atau liriknya sudah ada dari soundtrack aslinya, Adriana juga membuat lagu original yang melodi, lirik, serta aransemennya benar-benar ia buat sendiri. Meskipun tetap saja sih terinsipirasi dari unsur fandom tertentu seperti lagu berjudul Daughter of The Moon yang terinspirasi dari Princess Yue, karakter dari Avatar: The Last Air Bender yang berubah menjadi bulan untuk menyelamatkan banyak orang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZW25nrh-mxo\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47238\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47238\" data-attachment-id=\"47238\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yuk-tonton-gadis-gadis-kecil-menari/attachment/ariana6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ariana6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Princess Yue (Sumber: fanpop)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47238\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47238\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Princess Yue (Sumber: fanpop)</p></div></p>\n<p>Adriana sendiri menyebut lagu-lagunya sebagai “magically nerdy” melalui laman <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/adrisaurus\">patreon</a> miliknya. Tidak salah juga karena memang aransemen serta suaranya bisa menyihir orang-orang “nerd” untuk kembali merasakaan “feels” mereka terhadap karakter atau kejadian tertentu dalam game, buku, atau tv series kesukaannya. Apalagi suaranya memang cocok untuk lagu-lagu dark dan slow dengan lirik yang biasanya erat dengan unsur-unsur cerita angst, konten sedih nan menyakitkan dan cenderung menyiksa yang entah kenapa sangat dinikmati beberapa orang termasuk penulis (tapi bukan berarti masokis ya).</p>\n<p>Untuk mendengarkan karya Adriana, selain melalui youtube, beberapa lagu Adriana juga bisa diakses melalui i-Tunes dan Spotify dengan mencari nama adrisaurus pada aplikasi tersebut, sementara lagu-lagu lamanya juga bisa di download melalui link yang terdapat pada setiap video sehingga bisa dinikmati kapan saja tanpa bergantung pada koneksi internet.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47235\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47235\" data-attachment-id=\"47235\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/yuk-tonton-gadis-gadis-kecil-menari/attachment/ariana3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"ariana3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Adriana Figueroa (Sumber: adrisaurus)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47235\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ariana3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47235\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Adriana Figueroa (Sumber: adrisaurus)</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"73d7a138-c92d-5dbd-8843-fc4c973fb958"}}}